Koldskaal - a Danish summer dessert

By Jack Pedersen, September 17, 2016

5 tbsp sugar
A pinch of vanilla
3 eggs
1L buttermilk
1L ymer
Kammerjunkers

Whip 2 egg yolks with the sugar and the vanilla thoroughly.
Add an egg and whip again.
Mix with the buttermilk and ymer.
Whip 2 egg whites thoroughly and gently stir into the mixture.

Serve cold with kammerjunkers.